CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 19, 1958, pg. 14 reads: "Guest Speaker And Friends - When Andrew M. Bradley spoke Sunday at Kay Boys Club, ending National Boys' Week observance, his host was Councilman Paul F. Jones, left. Mrs. Charles Page was mistress of ceremonies at the program held at the club. Later, Attorney Jones gave a reception for Mr. Bradley at Terrace Hall Hotel. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Paul F. Jones, Mary Jane Mitchell Page, and Andrew M. Bradley posed in Kay Boys Club during National Boy's Week program
